   from <%= @event.start_time.strftime("%H:%M") %> to <%= @event.end_time.strftime("%H:%M") %>.
</p>
<p>
  If you're free to join, click <a href="<%= @confirmation_url %>">here</a> to confirm.
</p>
<p>
  If you're busy on that date, click <a href="<%= @decline_url %>">here</a>
    and we'll invite you to the next available workshop.
</p>
<p>
  If you don't want a bike anymore, click <a href="<%= @cancel_url %>">here</a>
   and we'll remove you from the list.
</p>

